002package com.commercetools.api.models.standalone_price;
003
004import com.commercetools.api.models.Referencable;
005import com.commercetools.api.models.ResourceIdentifiable;
006
007public interface StandalonePriceMixin extends Referencable<StandalonePrice>, ResourceIdentifiable<StandalonePrice> {
008    @Override
009    public default StandalonePriceResourceIdentifier toResourceIdentifier() {
010        return StandalonePriceResourceIdentifier.builder().id(getId()).build();
011    }
012
013    @Override
014    public default StandalonePriceReference toReference() {
015        return StandalonePriceReference.builder().id(getId()).build();
016    }
017}
